How to prepare linux FFP XWindows Program for PP : 
    1. Add Programmable Pipeline related Frame Buffer attributes into FrameBuffer attributes array.
    2. Accordingly find FBConfigs supporting these FrameBuffer attributes.
    3. From above multiple FBConfigs, find that one which has :
        a) Matching visualInfo
        b) Sample buffers to store samples
        c) More than 0 samples
        We will call this FBConfig as best FB config
    4. From this best FBConfigs, create VisualInfo
    5. From this VisualInfo and the best FBConfig, create the final glxContext and as usual make it current